latestIgtvVideos.title: My COVID Vaccine experience
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Covid Vaccine Experience 

1. Register on cowin.gov.in 

2. You can go to under45.in and join the telegram channel for real time updates on slot availability 

3. Please carry Aadhar card and Appointment slip to the vaccinated centre 

4. Please keep a copy of the Vaccination Certificate. Hard copy is handed over at the centre or you might download it from the website later 

5. I had mild fever, body cache and fatigue afterwards. It’s a natural response of the body nothing to worry

Share this with someone who might have questions
